snippet.title: Xeno Command Official Trailer
snippet.description:
New game announcement!!👏#XenoCommand is an #RTS game fused with #roguelike elements. Here you can lead a strong army with powerful heroes to defend the galaxy against Alien invasion in the challenging battles.

In the era of interstellar colonization, planets are in crisis. Heroes from different factions stand out to lead powerful armies against aliens and rescue the sufferers. You, the savior of the galaxy, are going to be the hero. Lead your army and combat alien invasions!

Our FaceBook page👉 https://www.facebook.com/XenoCommandGame
